Detailed Description

The structure is used to hold all the dpu configurations that were constructed at the time of pre-start configuration, so that they do not need to be reconstructed when issuing for the purpose of reconfiguration within sub-frame dpus or across sub-frames due to overlapping h/w resources (e.g L3 and core Local memory).
